    antlr.collections.AST, java.io.Serializable, ExpectedTypeAwareNode, InitializeableNode, SelectExpression

    public class SimpleCaseNode
extends AbstractSelectExpression
implements SelectExpression, ExpectedTypeAwareNode
    Models what ANSI SQL terms a simple case statement. This is a CASE expression in the form
     CASE [expression]
     WHEN [firstCondition] THEN [firstResult]
     WHEN [secondCondition] THEN [secondResult]
     ELSE [defaultResult]
 END
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
